Melee units other than War Elepthant throw torches when they attack Buildings, Sieges, and Ships. Villager and Fire Lancer uses their unique version of torch.
Torch status will automatically update upon advancing age, and it has nothing to do with the upgrade status of each unit. Every melee unit throws the same torch of age they are in.
Exceptions are Villager and Fire Lancer. Their torch damage does not change over ages.
